{"tid":411952,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"見到而家啲細路10個有8個都係講蝗語","createTime":"2017-09-24T08:50:03.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-11T01:12:53.000Z","uid":18245,"like":159,"dislike":6,"uniUserReply":9,"replies":[{"pid":"774631fefa7dc3a6cba87deafac29e4fb96b54ed","tid":411952,"uid":18245,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:50:03.000Z","msg":"見到而家啲細路10個有8個都係講蝗語 真係好恐怖 <br />\n蝗語教學推行左後 廣東話既地位越漸下降<br />\n可以想像到咁樣落去既話 唔洗好耐 廣東話就會完全被取代<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n「要消滅一個民族，首先要瓦解它的文化；要瓦解它的文化，首先先消滅承載它的語言；要消滅這種語言，首先先從他們的學校裏下手。」<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我地面對緊既唔單單係資源分配造成既住屋 學位 床位.etc既問題 <br />\n我地面對緊既係<span style=\"color: red;\">Extinction</span> 香港民族比人消滅緊啊<br />\n政府高層全部唔係我地既人 法治亦淪為佢地消滅民眾聲音既工具 <br />\n而家既殖民政府係利用緊我地青春 時間 金錢 我地既人生 去養緊班蝗 洗腦我地既下一代  仲用我地既手去消滅我地既民族  <br />\n<br />\n<br />\n殖民政府腐敗無能 已經唔可能由內而外改革<br />\n入邊全部都係佢地既人 成班賣國賊 最近仲有隻佢地既走狗揚言要殺我地<br />\n<br />\n為左我地自己既人生<br />\n為保護我地出生既香港<br />\n為保護我地既下一代免受支共既極權統治<br />\n<br />\n唯有獨立建國 建立一個真正屬於香港人既香港 <br />\n一個讓你感到自豪既香港<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://img.eservice-hk.net/upload/2017/09/07/012443_620a5c4061cf7ddb561ce7fd18caea7d.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fimg.eservice-hk.net%2Fupload%2F2017%2F09%2F07%2F012443_620a5c4061cf7ddb561ce7fd18caea7d.jpg&h=b55238aa&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n支持香港獨立 必須由保護我地既語言做起"},{"pid":"5b3add7ca2ea3c4baeb3efd0d417262411639f94","tid":411952,"uid":20563,"like":15,"dislike":2,"score":13,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:52:44.000Z","msg":"聽到要大聲屌柒d 大陸仔叫佢地d 大陸喱返鄉下<br />\n屌到佢地怕就唔會講蝗語"},{"pid":"f8037c4ae4d1ab27e5cea3969ceab76176813581","tid":411952,"uid":35696,"like":3,"dislike":1,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T08:52:52.000Z","msg":"試過中小學放學時間搭東鐵去大埔墟以北嘅站<br />\n成架車好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9075bb3bd9b8b920e9406494d81d93b0d5035585","tid":411952,"uid":37463,"like":11,"dislike":1,"score":10,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:04:23.000Z","msg":"事關非普教既小學<br />\n學校將蝗語班定位為&quot;精英班&quot;<br />\nd細路會死講蝗語做母語<br />\n<br />\n你留意下 , 班細路係精通廣東話(父母係香港人講廣東話) , 但同d fd溝通係用蝗語<br />\n<br />\n支共洗血已經完全成功<br />\n得返最後呢幾代中學生做真香港人真係好可悲"},{"pid":"339edb6b694b2c74764d2eb3864f599efe164a09","tid":411952,"uid":82125,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:11:47.000Z","msg":"之前好似話係每級一班用蝗語教學，但我問過樓下班小學生，佢地3年班開始已經全部用蝗語教中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實香港人可以點捍衛自己既語言？我都想係呢方面出份力"},{"pid":"982e5a28b32d1cc219082c17f31b0bc15b2a39f1","tid":411952,"uid":82829,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:19:58.000Z","msg":"小學用蝗語中學用返粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f38b076465c886af4295bcd949a62820f7fa9d74","tid":411952,"uid":41245,"like":2,"dislike":1,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:21:36.000Z","msg":"所以大學學生會一定要守住廣東話<br />\n城大好似冇本地組莊"},{"pid":"1fbd39e9b67115a27162145a31669c62a48a54e4","tid":411952,"uid":37463,"like":1,"dislike":1,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:22:13.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>之前好似話係每級一班用蝗語教學，但我問過樓下班小學生，佢地3年班開始已經全部用蝗語教中文<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n<br />\n其實香港人可以點捍衛自己既語言？我都想係呢方面出份力</blockquote><br />\n咪就係精英班 ...<br />\n所以呢個政策好仆街 , 個問題根本比國教更嚴重<br />\n你諗下 , 小朋友/家長都想叻過人 , 爭入精英班 , 變相要自學蝗語令到唔讀都流利"},{"pid":"cc5e1f6c8575644dfb5b616fd78eb7c1abb27415","tid":411952,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":3,"score":-3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:23:29.000Z","msg":"前幾日聽到兩個大約中三，四女生講蝗語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9517350a4a19b7aa9b66a4fd28e55a38b6cb3873","tid":411952,"uid":41245,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:24:33.000Z","msg":"<a href=\"https://www.facebook.com/AlvisChan1209/posts/1591148770905649\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.facebook.com%2FAlvisChan1209%2Fposts%2F1591148770905649&d=gvPQCd7LuzKh4Sy6KYKq1TQ9OVC7k%2FvddpU5ARN7O10%3D&h=b12e9961\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://www.facebook.com/AlvisChan1209/posts/1591148770905649</a>"},{"pid":"c125ac6f2eab2498a43c62038fc76bfb84cdfba0","tid":411952,"uid":129753,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:39:39.000Z","msg":"暑假時去咗好多中小學校做裝修，真係好撚多細路講蝗語。試過係一間中學做裝修，D學生一放學成村人行落黎聽到8成人都講蝗語。<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"98d19d26b619bbd25820fe98c24bdbc004485569","tid":411952,"uid":20241,"like":1,"dislike":6,"score":-5,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T09:45:07.000Z","msg":"你都識得講當權者全部都係對面既人<br />\n你想點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倒不如真係集合一班人移民去其他地方保留番香港既血脈啦"},{"pid":"5b509056bc0c3ecb5c368ecb0293021c8567dc04","tid":411952,"uid":82125,"like":4,"dislike":1,"score":3,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-24T11:23:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識得講當權者全部都係對面既人<br />\n你想點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倒不如真係集合一班人移民去其他地方保留番香港既血脈啦</blockquote><br />\n去到第二個國家就應該係我地融入人地，而唔係我地繼續自己既文化，如果唔係變左我地係蝗蟲，不過講就易，望下自己個銀行戶口，應該去邊都難<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"253b90eef2044043ffc03a9edf0c145c16d408a5","tid":411952,"uid":53026,"like":2,"dislike":0,"score":2,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:15:34.000Z","msg":"唔明，點解英文中小學又唔會得閒無事講英文？"},{"pid":"6d90f420c0a7b40fdd5ee7278f90d53105f3548f","tid":411952,"uid":38671,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:20:58.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>唔明，點解英文中小學又唔會得閒無事講英文？</blockquote><br />\n因為普教中唔只課堂講普通話<br />\n平時同新移民同學傾計同玩都係講普通話"},{"pid":"9a20936f1d88aa535c7581316adbafddbd0425b8","tid":411952,"uid":71864,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:26:09.000Z","msg":"琴日去完上水先知<br />\n<br />\n北區真係另一個世界"},{"pid":"5aa6fd178769aa33cafa67ca011b524573417ddd","tid":411952,"uid":104443,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:31:59.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>你都識得講當權者全部都係對面既人<br />\n你想點搞<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n倒不如真係集合一班人移民去其他地方保留番香港既血脈啦</blockquote><br />\n<span style=\"color: red;\"><span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\">臺灣獨立係死五毛</span></span>"},{"pid":"3987b4e1083bb709f692920da2947168408a7c2f","tid":411952,"uid":30972,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T02:40:43.000Z","msg":"去深水埗食m記 屌佢老味 啲中學生講蝗話㗎<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/fire.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"28e7ef2fa971c21e80e59d16e2e13074f2f3d9de","tid":411952,"uid":37413,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:07:24.000Z","msg":"啲父母先仆街，明明土生土長香港人<br />\n不斷同個仔講蝗語訓練佢哋，話將來有錢途啲<br />\n屌佢老母！"},{"pid":"d6fbdf0fa2b4722affc45171fb6e67246718ef16","tid":411952,"uid":131157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-25T03:55:29.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"d34248a2b1d778a8e952dee8eacee0ca0fb49f31","tid":411952,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:42:11.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>試過中小學放學時間搭東鐵去大埔墟以北嘅站<br />\n成架車好恐怖<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n今日行經上環<br />\n一班小學生放左學用蝗語傾計<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"3ae439c8a692ffe8662019dc329fe3ea52c796a4","tid":411952,"uid":35696,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:53:14.000Z","msg":"其實可唔可以利用法庭釐定廣東話係香港嘅地位？<br />\n法定語言中嘅中文係指廣府話<br />\n所有官員，政府公布 絕大多數都係用廣東話<br />\n電視台入面嘅中文台都係為廣東話使用者而設<br />\n街名更加係証據 例如 深圳街 英文係Shamchun Street<br />\n<br />\n而支那話深圳英文係Shenzhen<br />\n所有香港英文音釋嘅名都係以廣東話做基礎"},{"pid":"572423afb63501a06fb5e6b9317b55c337a3d385","tid":411952,"uid":10788,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-26T12:54:38.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>小學用蝗語中學用返粵語<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/agree.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n太天真"},{"pid":"6a4de33b0e93f944a4604a648e87ee21765a2815","